---------------------------------------------------------------(with shield pvp)
autocrit - spam click attack button while holding shield towards enemy
stunning - disabling shield and instantly hitting them
backstab - instantaneous jump behind/sideways the enemy landing a crit
shield-melee - releasing shield with sword attack and holding shield again
crit-shield-melee - shield-melee with critical attack

---------------------------------------------------------------
when a armed shield is hit by an axe then its gets disabled for 5 secs
